release.notes:
Recorded, mixed & mastered @ The Blasting Room; Ft. Collins, CO.; June 15-July 20th 2000, while the mountains burned a bright orange. 
Additional recording @ Orange Whip and The Crank Lab; Santa Barbara, CA.
